  "critical": false,
  "description": "Focused electron beam (30-150kV accelerating voltage, 10-100mA beam current) welding in vacuum chamber. Deep narrow penetration (depth-to-width 10:1 to 30:1), minimal heat input and distortion. Zero porosity, zero contamination. Critical for UHV vacuum chamber fabrication (leak rates ≤10⁻¹⁰ mbar·L/s), refractory metals, and aerospace components. Single-pass penetration up to 200mm in steel.",
